  title="Buying Property in Brisbane's Inner East: A Buyer's Guide | Daniel Gierach"
  description="A practical guide to buying property in Brisbane's inner east: suburbs, property types, value drivers, market conditions, due diligence, and how to prepare."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
