        <a href="/buyers" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.85rem 1.6rem;background:#b98229;color:#fff;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;">Register as a buyer &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</article>

